Subject: [PATCH] KVM: Destroy target device if coalesced MMIO unregistration
 fails
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: b1cb1fac22abf102ffeb29dd3eeca208a3869d54
